Download logo President His Highness Sheikh Khalifa bin Zayed Al Nahyan has sent a message of congratulations to President Mahamadou Issoufou of Niger on the occasion of his country's Republic Day celebrations, marked on 18th December.  His Highness Sheikh Mohammed bin Rashid Al Maktoum, Vice President, Prime Minister and Ruler of Dubai, and His Highness Sheikh Mohamed bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Crown Prince of Abu Dhabi and Deputy Supreme Commander of the UAE Armed Forces, sent similar messages to President Issoufou. Their Highnesses also sent congratulatory messages to Niger's Prime Minister, Brigi Rafini. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of United Arab Emirates Ministry of Foreign Affairs & International Coperation.